    <section>
        <h>uses</h>
        <section id="uses-predicate">
            <h>predicate</h>
            <p>Like other adjectives, <g>bàn</g> can be used (uninflected) as the predicate of the
                verb <a href="?gd=bi"><g>bi</g></a>.</p>
            <p>Some examples – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha Màiri <m>bàn</m>.</gd>
                        <tr>Mary is fair-haired.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 8 [adapted]</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>A bheil an cat <m>bàn</m>?</gd>
                        <tr>Is the cat white?</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 15</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </section>
        <section id="uses-mod">
            <h>modifier</h>
            <p>Like other adjectives, <g>bàn</g> can be used as a post-modifier of a <a
                    href="?xx=nouns/nouns">noun</a>.</p>
            <p>Some examples with masculine nouns – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>A bheil <m>falt bàn</m> air Seumas?</gd>
                        <tr>Does James have fair hair?</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 13–14</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Càit a bheil an <m>cat bàn</m> an diugh?</gd>
                        <tr>Where is the white cat today?</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 14</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
            <p>When the modified noun is feminine, <g>bàn</g> is lenited to <g>bhàn</g> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha <m>Màiri bhàn</m> anns an achadh an diugh.</gd>
                        <tr>Fair-headed Mary is in the field today.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 9 [adapted]</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
            <p>Note the difference in meaning between the following examples – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha Màiri beag bàn.</gd>
                        <tr>Mary is small and fair-haired.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 8</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha Màiri bheag bàn.</gd>
                        <tr>Little Mary is fair-haired.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 8</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </section>
